# Notion API Configuration
# 
# 1. Create an integration at: https://www.notion.so/my-integrations
# 2. Copy the "Internal Integration Token" and paste it below as NOTION_SECRET
# 3. Find your parent page ID:
#    - Open the page in Notion
#    - Click "Share" → "Copy link"
#    - Extract the 32-character ID from the URL
#    - Example: https://notion.so/My-Page-abc123def456...
#    - Page ID: abc123def456...
# 4. IMPORTANT: Grant the integration access to your page:
#    - Open the parent page in Notion
#    - Click "..." (more options) → "Add connections"
#    - Select your integration from the list
#    - Without this step, you'll get "restricted_resource" errors!

NOTION_SECRET=your_notion_integration_token_here
NOTION_PARENT_PAGE_ID=your_target_parent_page_id_here
